title: Gumming up the works over Benghazi
text: ANALYSIS/OPINION: Pity the American voter. Angry, frustrated and desperate, in successive elections he delivers more Republican soldiers to Congress, all in the spirit of Dr. Johnson's famous description of a second marriage as " the triumph of hope over experience. " All that changes in Washington is the size of the nothingburgers. ... ...
